data.description: Welcome to a rare opportunity in this highly sought-after neighborhood. This stunning cul-de-sac location boasts an owned solar system, making it an exceptional find. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers plenty of space for comfortable living. The estate-sized lot spans over 9,174 square feet and features a practical floorplan with an open concept layout. Enjoy the spacious yard and relax on the covered patio while taking advantage of stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen. Located close to shopping options, convenience is at your fingertips. Don't miss the nice master bath with a jetted tub or the newer AC condenser installed for added comfort and efficiency. Trust us, you won't want to miss out on this incredible opportunity.
